text: SKD may refer to: *Airline abbreviated term for Schedule. *IATA airport code for Samarkand Airport in Samarkand, Uzbekistan *Semi Knocked Down, a kit containing parts needed to assemble a product *Science Ki Duniya, a magazine *Slovenski krščanski demokrati (Slovene Christian Democrats), Slovene political party * SKDKnickerbocker, American public relations firm *Shaun Kenny-Dowall, rugby league footballer
title: SKD
